{
  "stem": "2723.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Level two is, I think, what we were working on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my work consisted of being assigned to a foreman, together with about five others, who didn't all come with me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were already there or came before me from other places, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Um, they didn't look too bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Obviously, they were getting slightly more to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I remember the name of the man who I was assigned to was Mr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Peitch, with a German spelling, P-E-I-T-C-H.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was very, very polite.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I hoped that maybe my luck will change.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He was, however, not really polite.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He was just a machine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He knew how to behave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he didn't quite know how to modify his behavior to us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He didn't know who-- what to do with us, how to handle us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He was so mystified by appearance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had different prison clothes in that factory, no more attractive, but slightly less bizarre, perhaps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were marked with a cross at the back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I'm quite sure that this must have been some kind of attempt at humane behavior.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because I developed a very bad ear infection.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And because I had no hair, it was very visible that pus was pouring from my ear.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And it stank to high heaven.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the people in charge complained that I was smelly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And one day-- I was quite sure that this was the end of me-- I was told that I'm going to be taken to a doctor.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There was nobody like that on that particular set-up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And very early in the morning, I was taken by train with three others who needed medical treatment.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was a bizarre, bizarre occurrence, in my recollection.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
